          "alt": "IMG_7090"
        }}></img></a></p>
    <p>{`We went by 7/11 and grabbed some Thai beers, took a tuk-tuk back home to our hotel (which is an exhilarating experience, where you just don’t think about safety, and then lounged the rest of the evening away on our poolside patio. I think we are going to like this place!`}</p>

